The Empire star,Jussie Smollett,is donating a lot of cash to charities for the holiday season.According to TMZ, Jussie is paying the money to groups like the Black AIDS Institute, Flint KIDS, South Africa’s SKY Foundation, the Trayvon Martin Foundation, the Human Rights Campaign, Know Your Rights Camp, ACLU and the Anthony Burrell Dance School. The American singer and actor began his career has a child actor in 1987. Jussie is a recipeint of the 2016 NAACP Image Awards of various categories: Outstanding song,Outstanding new artist,Outstanding actor in a Drama series and many other nominations for his works.